data.description: Explore this attractive and conveniently located 3-bedroom split level home in the heart of the Town of Poughkeepsie! Upon entering, you'll discover an eat-in kitchen equipped with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and a large pantry closet. Hardwood floors flow seamlessly throughout the main level, connecting three comfortable bedrooms and a generously sized living room. A gas fireplace adds a cozy touch to the living area. The master bedroom features a fully remodeled bathroom and a spacious walk-in closet. Abundant natural light fills the interior, thanks to the vaulted ceilings and strategically placed skylights. The lower level offers an expansive family room, complete with a laundry area, and an additional bonus room that can serve various purposes. Outside, the property provides ample space for outdoor enjoyment, with a sizable trex deck, a charming paver patio, and a spacious fenced backyard, perfect for summer entertaining. Located less than one mile from Route 9, you'll have easy access to shopping and dining options, making this home not only inviting but also conveniently positioned. Don't miss the opportunity to make this wonderful property your new home!
